 way to be considered for suitable opportunities is by uploading your details to our online database, visit careers.amecfw.comCan’t find the information you’re looking for at amecfw.com/early-careers? Use this if you have any queries about our graduate, apprentice, intern or work experience programmes.Fraudsters contact people who are looking for work and offer jobs, posing as Amec Foster Wheeler We treat such abuse seriously and any reports of such fraudulent activity are dealt with by our own security team, often in conjunction with legal organisations and law enforcement, as appropriate.If you believe you are the victim of a recruitment scam, please report it here.If you would like to become a registered supplier of goods or services to Amec Foster Wheeler please visit amecfw.com/suppliers where you can register via our supplier portal. This is the only way to be considered for our supply chain.Use this form if you have any further queries regarding supply chain management.Looking for an Amec Foster Wheeler office or telephone number?Please visit amecfw.com/offices for a full list of our locations worldwideUse this form for any queries relating to invoices and payments.Sign up to receive our media alerts at media.amecfw.com/media-alerts Alternatively, use this form if you have any queries regarding news from Amec Foster WheelerIf your query doesn’t relate to any of the other categories, please use this form.   This field is requiredThis field is requiredThis email address is not validThis field is requiredWhat does your query relate to? What does your query relate to? CareersGraduates, apprentices, interns, work experienceRecruitment scamSupply chainOffices/locationsInvoices/paymentsMediaGeneral enquiryThis field is requiredThis field is requiredThis field is requiredPlease do not use this form for job enquiries. Visit careers.amecfw.comPlease do not use this form for general career enquiries. Visit careers.amecfw.comPlease do not use this form for job enquiries.