                    Describing Amec Foster Wheeler? Excellence in delivery, a highly-integrated and people oriented business, producing high-value solutions for our customers
                









                    Our values are a declaration of our core beliefs and the defining features of our culture that breeds achievement
                









                    Sustainability development is shaping our business everyday; it is at the heart of Amec Foster Wheeler’s values
                









                    Our vision is to be the most trusted partner for our customers by consistently delivering excellence - bringing together the knowledge, expertise and skills of our people from across our global network
                







