Amec Foster Wheeler plc

76-78 Old St. 
London  EC1V 9RU United Kingdom
Phone: +44 20 ____ ____
Fax: +44 20 ____ ____
http://www.amec.com





47
Managers




157
IT employees




$275.2MEST.
IT Budget




AMEC is a British company that provides consultancy, engineering and project management services. These services are specifically for the oil and gas, mining, power generation, nuclear, process and water industries.
• Maintains a £100,000-£250,000 web development contract.
• Maintains a £1M-£5M data center operations contract.

2013 and Earlier:
AMEC is a British company that provides consultancy, engineering and project management services. These services are specifically for the oil and gas, mining, power generation,… More• Maintains a £100,000-£250,000 web development contract.
• Maintains a £1M-£5M data center operations contract.

2013 and Earlier:
AMEC is a British company that provides consultancy, engineering and project management services. These services are specifically for the oil and gas, mining, power generation, nuclear, process and water industries.

IT Priorities
• In 2013, the company is hiring multiple IT project managers to define and implement systems and provide systems solutions and application support at various locations.
• AMEC plc will be starting on a project for the implementation of new Microsoft web servers.

IT Structure
• At AMEC, the IT department is primarily centralized at the headquarters in London, UK. 
• With over 40 offices throughout the UK, and more across the globe, the department is spread out where its main focuses are managing systems and supporting IT environments. 
• Within the company a majority of the staff supports the director of IT and maintains information management operations, ensuring databases are running properly. 
• Other areas of focus are the day-to-day IT operations, infrastructure, global change and help desk support.
• A Cheshire office contains a wide amount of IT staff responsible for business systems, acting as a liaison between the IT and business departments. Database administration is also managed at this location. AMEC has a large amount of IT in the US and Canada as well.





