Amec Foster Wheeler - Wikipedia






















 






Amec Foster Wheeler

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

See also: AMEC (disambiguation)

Amec Foster Wheeler





Type

Public limited company


Traded as
LSE: AMFW NYSE: AMFW


